{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:49:17.371162+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: b71670149e6593f858aad3d5d40d755578785ca2)", "id": "lc_145781ae-960e-4a02-bd70-dc4da65a92e9"}, {"type": "text", "text": "---\nid: getting-started\ntitle: Getting Started\n---\n\n# Getting Started\n\nUse this page to explain how to run the documentation site locally.\n", "id": "lc_82888114-678f-4c5e-b815-14c40cb52dec"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "ea0287cf-8aec-4207-a497-68fe614a10a3", "tool_call_id": "call_d6432c42e41940049c6d4341", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:49:17.379968+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 439672d72a3ae56a51725fc19de5cbf4e12f69f8)", "id": "lc_a3fc30e4-7438-43b1-afb8-6de5093e9550"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# Product Documentation Portal\n\nA Docusaurus documentation portal for product setup guides, installation notes, and maintenance documentation.\n\n## Project layout\n\n- `docs/` — Documentation pages rendered by Docusaurus.\n- `docusaurus.config.js` — Site configuration.\n- `sidebars.js` — Sidebar navigation.\n- `package.json` — Node scripts and dependencies.\n\n## Quick start\n\n```bash\nmake validate\n```\n```bash\nnpm install\n```\n```bash\nnpm run build\n```\n\n## Documentation workflow\n\n1. Add or update Markdown pages under `docs/`.\n2. Keep `sidebars.js` synchronized with new pages.\n3. Validate JavaScript config before opening a PR.\n4. Run a full Docusaurus build before release.\n\n## Maintenance notes\n\nUse the sidebar configuration when adding or moving documentation pages.\n\n## Contributing\n\nKeep changes focused, update documentation when behavior changes, and run the validation commands before submitting a pull request.\n", "id": "lc_47d53a6a-5740-4105-8cc9-678443f8445f"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "c1acad3c-f4ba-458b-a17c-c04aac3608dc", "tool_call_id": "call_495b5d0cf771405d8b4da886", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
